title: Odd Moves
description:
Pablo Torre, Israel Gutierrez and The Ringer's Kevin Clark debate their biggest takeaways from The Athletic’s piece on Urban Meyer’s tenure in Jacksonville and their thoughts on the Deshaun Watson trade and his new contract.
